cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a face Re-ID system for Human-Robot Interaction.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper employs Deep Convolutional Neural Networks for feature extraction.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the proposed system is intended for use in social robots, which require tailored interaction strategies based on individual user preferences.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques for face Re-ID.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also relevant as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed system on video datasets.
